{"tid":978711,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"環保撚剩係識叫人走膠，空氣污染唔講？","createTime":"2019-01-12T06:29:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T16:01:34.000Z","uid":23754,"like":93,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"7ea9de2742c8f3032770efb0f3518436bd0a65fd","tid":978711,"uid":23754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T06:29:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日個天灰蒙蒙<br />\n陸上嘅生物都好慘呀，吸晒啲懸浮粒子<br />\n但環保撚剩係講啲海洋生物食膠，真係好唔公平！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n為咗天空嘅飛鳥，陸上嘅走獸<br />\n<br />\n我地應該出一分力提議全面禁止使用交通工具，全部香港人行路返工<br />\n全面禁止所有建築物開冷氣<br />\n全面禁止用電<br />\n<br />\n走車走電走冷氣<br />\n仲有無咩可以走？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d6ad720b2f40162256dcb973ba57a423152c7c","tid":978711,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":35,"score":-35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T06:32:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1cd70173f3c2e2eadaf7ceaa37f9d5de6483fd9","tid":978711,"uid":90476,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T06:32:32.000Z","msg":"環保撚，我屌你老母！"},{"pid":"1aea40b461f070e04db3a6a3572fccaec12005d9","tid":978711,"uid":161263,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T06:34:20.000Z","msg":"根本走飲管就解決唔到啲咩大問題<br />\n最影響到地球環境既班環保膠視而不見"},{"pid":"ccef3374dde7c66dc6875b0a86337e0042eefa43","tid":978711,"uid":101900,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f1cd70173f3c2e2eadaf7ceaa37f9d5de6483fd9","tid":978711,"uid":90476,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T06:32:32.000Z","msg":"環保撚，我屌你老母！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T06:34:56.000Z","msg":"環乜撚野保<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成班衝出黎柒"},{"pid":"73c07cc6b068f799f1f807c079cf9bdc6bf2c8e3","tid":978711,"uid":23754,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"1aea40b461f070e04db3a6